                "content": "Borrower is connected to Loan.",
                "img_id": null
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "role": "paragraph",
        "segment": "Since higher coupling and lower cohesion generally make a class harder to modify, it is reasonable to assume that the class Loan will probably be harder to modify than class Borrower.",
        "citations": []
    },
    {
        "role": "sentence",
        "segment": "Therefore, the correct answer is b. It will probably be harder to modify than class Borrower.",
        "citations": []
